### ============================================
### ACTUALIZAR CERVEZA
### ============================================

### Actualizar cerveza 1 (reemplaza con un ID real)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/cervezas/69c2c8696c5225d9cbc91f89
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "nombre": "Estrella Damm Editada",
  "descripcion": "Cerveza lager catalana de sabor suave y refrescante",
  "graduacion": 5.4,
  "tipo": "Lager"
}

###

### Actualizar cerveza 2 (reemplaza con un ID real)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/cervezas/507f1f77bcf86cd799439012
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "nombre": "Guinness Editada",
  "descripcion": "Versión editada de la stout irlandesa más famosa",
  "graduacion": 4.2,
  "tipo": "Stout"
}

### ============================================
### ELIMINAR CERVEZA
### ============================================

### Eliminar cerveza 1 (reemplaza con un ID real)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/cervezas/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Eliminar cerveza 2 (reemplaza con un ID real)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/cervezas/69c2da35f47d71fa2ccac852
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}